---
import BaseLayout from '../components/BaseLayout.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Home" description="COPPA readiness for technology companies. Protect children's privacy and meet FTC requirements.">
  <HeroSection
    headline="COPPA Readiness for Technology Companies"
    subheadline="Protect children's privacy. Meet FTC requirements. Build trust with parents and schools."
    ctaText="Get Started"
    ctaHref="/about"
  />

  <section class="content section">
    <h2>Why COPPA Matters</h2>
    <p>Children's online privacy is under increasing regulatory scrutiny. Companies whose products or services may be used by children under 13 face strict FTC enforcement, reputational risk, and the responsibility to earn the trust of parents and educators.</p>
    <div class="value-grid">
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Protect Children's Privacy</h3>
        <p>COPPA is the primary federal law governing children's online privacy. It requires verifiable parental consent before collecting personal information from children under 13.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Avoid FTC Enforcement</h3>
        <p>The FTC actively enforces COPPA with penalties reaching millions of dollars. Non-compliance creates significant financial and reputational exposure.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Enable Safe Harbor Participation</h3>
        <p>COPPA safe harbor programs provide streamlined compliance paths and industry-specific guidance, reducing regulatory uncertainty for qualifying companies.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Build Parental Trust</h3>
        <p>Demonstrating COPPA compliance builds confidence with parents and schools, opening doors to the education technology and children's content markets.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content section">
    <h2>How We Help</h2>
    <p>Four service packages designed to meet you where you are in your compliance journey.</p>
    <div class="service-overview-grid">
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Readiness Sprint</h3>
        <p>Scope, assess, and plan in 2&#8211;4 weeks</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Remediation Program</h3>
        <p>Close gaps and build your evidence machine</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Audit Support</h3>
        <p>Expert coordination during audit fieldwork</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Continuous Compliance</h3>
        <p>Stay audit-ready year-round</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content section cta-section">
    <h2>Ready to Get Started?</h2>
    <p>Whether you're building a children's product for the first time or strengthening existing COPPA practices, we can help you design compliant consent flows, audit third-party SDKs, and earn the trust of parents and educators.</p>
    <a href="/about" class="cta-button">Let's Talk</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .value-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .value-item {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .value-item h3 {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .value-item p {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .service-overview-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .service-overview-card {
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: block;
  }

  .service-overview-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-heading);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .service-overview-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem var(--spacing-page);
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }

  .cta-section p {
    max-width: 36rem;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .value-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .service-overview-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .service-overview-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
